altTitle: 幼馴染の妹の家庭教師をはじめたら 疎遠だった幼馴染が怖い
When I start being a home tutor for my childhood friend’s younger sister, the unfriendly childhood friend is angry ~I am completely unaware that she – my high school idol – likes me
title: Osananajimi no Imouto no Kateikyoushi wo Hajimetara Soen Datta Osananajimi ga Kowai
